90
00:05:14,270 --> 00:05:15,150
Mother.

91
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,480
Enough.

92
00:05:17,430 --> 00:05:18,310
It's good now.

93
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,110
After going through so much,

94
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:23,520
