115
00:06:53,870 --> 00:06:54,750
Your Highness,

116
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,280
don't be angry.

117
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:06,280
I wrongly blamed you.

118
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,110
Lu Chang

119
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,470
