125
00:07:48,630 --> 00:07:52,720
You accused me of abusing authority.

126
00:07:55,390 --> 00:07:56,720
I'm your husband.

127
00:07:57,070 --> 00:07:57,950
How could you

128
00:07:58,750 --> 00:08:00,520
misunderstand me like this?

129
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,560
I've always spoken bluntly.

130
00:08:03,580 --> 00:08:04,720
I acted rashly

131
00:08:04,730 --> 00:08:06,680
for Mingshu's sake.

132
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,200
Don't you know me well?

133
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:15,110
I know I was wrong.

134
00:08:15,390 --> 00:08:16,640
Don't be angry.

135
00:08:17,190 --> 00:08:18,200
Dare you

136
00:08:18,430 --> 00:08:19,390
reduce my care for you

137
00:08:19,580 --> 00:08:20,870
to mere selfishness again?

138
00:08:21,570 --> 00:08:22,550
Never!

139
00:08:31,230 --> 00:08:32,210
Last warning.

140
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:35,960
Now,

141
00:08:36,390 --> 00:08:38,880
