142
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,280
What does that mean?

143
00:08:41,150 --> 00:08:42,070
Don't tell me...

144
00:08:43,030 --> 00:08:46,480
Exactly. Lu Chang is her chosen one.

145
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,790
Poor Qingzhao would suffer.

146
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,200
By the way,

147
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:54,160
does Lu Chang have a crush on Mingshu?

148
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,320
I'm

149
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:58,910
not sure about this,

150
00:08:59,250 --> 00:09:00,120
but he does

151
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,160
care a great deal

152
00:09:01,510 --> 00:09:02,520
about his sister.

153
00:09:04,150 --> 00:09:05,710
In that case,

154
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,790
we may as well do them a favor

155
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,710
and give them a push.

156
00:09:17,060 --> 00:09:21,140
(Top Scholar Residence)

157
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:26,960
Morning.

158
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,600
(Shuyue Pavilion)

159
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,480
Morning.

160
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,950
What are you doing at my door?

161
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,360
I'm waiting for you.

162
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:37,550
Why?

163
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,710
When we were in Jianglin,

164
00:09:40,010 --> 00:09:41,520
