165
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,150
I heard that Prince Zhao is hosting one

166
00:09:43,150 --> 00:09:45,120
at the Lan Garden tonight.

167
00:09:45,870 --> 00:09:46,910
Let's go and take a look.

168
00:09:47,910 --> 00:09:48,790
Ok.

169
00:09:49,030 --> 00:09:50,480
Let's go when you're off duty.

170
00:09:51,670 --> 00:09:52,550
Fine.

171
00:09:58,480 --> 00:10:00,670
The lanterns here are beautiful,

172
00:10:02,030 --> 00:10:03,760
especially that lantern bridge.

173
00:10:06,790 --> 00:10:09,910
Why is no one else here?

174
00:10:11,670 --> 00:10:13,240
Maybe it's too early,

175
00:10:13,390 --> 00:10:14,550
and people haven't come out yet.

176
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:20,360
Mingshu,

177
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:23,040
look at the lanterns on the bridge.

178
00:10:29,270 --> 00:10:30,150
Riddles.

179
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:32,120
Buddy, let's solve them!

180
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,190
There are so many.

181
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,070
Which one first?

182
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:44,360
The one beneath the fish lantern.

183
00:10:46,870 --> 00:10:48,040
It's easy.

184
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:53,950
(A Chinese character)
Look until the hair turns gray.

185
00:10:55,150 --> 00:10:56,670
"Gray hair" indicates a single stroke.

186
00:10:58,320 --> 00:11:00,160
"My", right?

187
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:04,120
Patience. Next.

188
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:16,070
(A Chinese character)
A small boat floats across the water.

189
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,360
"Heart".

190
00:11:19,870 --> 00:11:20,750
Clever.

191
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,320
Next one.

192
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:34,160
(A Chinese character)
Words unspoken, understood by heart.

193
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:37,240
Music floats, stirring hidden love.

194
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:39,670
This one is harder.

195
00:11:39,670 --> 00:11:40,550
Let me think.

196
00:11:49,550 --> 00:11:50,430
"Is".

197
00:11:52,870 --> 00:11:54,070
The last one.

198
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:12,360
(A Chinese character)
You have a woman as companion.

199
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,160
I can't solve it.

200
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,310
It's your turn.

201
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,360
The last character

202
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,080
is "yours".

203
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,120
Mingshu,

204
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:44,950
