213
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,550
I refuse to guess.

214
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:14,880
I need to hear it from your lips.

215
00:13:15,060 --> 00:13:17,600
♪Let mortal ties never fade♪

216
00:13:18,830 --> 00:13:21,480
♪As time quietly slips away♪

217
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:24,560
♪Don't let us miss growing old together♪

218
00:13:25,330 --> 00:13:27,330
♪May this heart stay true as the first day♪

219
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:29,040
You're the one

220
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,280
I could never let go of,

221
00:13:32,510 --> 00:13:33,710
