222
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:39,910
No matter your past

223
00:13:40,750 --> 00:13:41,910
or future,

224
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:45,430
I only wish to stay by your side,

225
00:13:47,390 --> 00:13:48,880
share every joy with you,

226
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,240
and never part from you.

227
00:13:56,790 --> 00:13:57,670
Mingshu,

228
00:13:59,550 --> 00:14:00,550
will you have me?

229
00:14:03,350 --> 00:14:06,320
♪If the moon above the sea is full♪

230
00:14:06,610 --> 00:14:09,400
♪Will you return♪

231
00:14:09,780 --> 00:14:12,700
♪In years left, wait for me♪

232
00:14:12,860 --> 00:14:15,800
♪With a beginning and an end♪

233
00:14:16,070 --> 00:14:19,100
♪May time inscribe our names♪

234
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:22,230
♪Where vows remain♪

235
00:14:22,550 --> 00:14:26,080
♪As if it were yesterday♪

236
00:14:48,580 --> 00:14:51,010
♪May life's towers stand tall♪

237
00:14:51,010 --> 00:14:53,500
♪With love that outlasts all♪

238
00:14:54,910 --> 00:14:57,450
♪Together we'll traverse♪

239
00:14:57,450 --> 00:15:00,630
♪Through grandeur and adversity♪

240
00:15:01,390 --> 00:15:03,850
♪When clarity arrives♪

241
00:15:03,850 --> 00:15:06,590
♪Destiny's threads entwine,
