243
00:15:07,850 --> 00:15:13,050
♪In glances back, our story's told♪

244
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:16,950
♪If all scenes fade to view♪

245
00:15:16,950 --> 00:15:19,880
♪Will you return♪

246
00:15:20,210 --> 00:15:22,970
♪Through years with sincere love♪

247
00:15:22,970 --> 00:15:26,130
♪May all enigmas grow clear♪

248
00:15:26,410 --> 00:15:29,700
♪Counting endless nights♪

249
00:15:29,700 --> 00:15:31,830
♪Yet never your♪

