00:15:31,830 --> 00:15:37,920
♪Silhouette in sight♪

251
00:15:40,780 --> 00:15:42,620
(Shuyue Pavilion)

252
00:15:42,640 --> 00:15:45,430
♪Will you return♪

253
00:15:45,810 --> 00:15:48,730
♪In years left, wait for me♪

254
00:15:48,890 --> 00:15:51,830
♪With a beginning and an end♪

255
00:15:52,100 --> 00:15:55,130
♪May time inscribe our names♪

