260
00:16:29,910 --> 00:16:31,480
Go to her room and check.

261
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:32,400
Wake her up.

262
00:16:33,750 --> 00:16:34,600
Go.

263
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:35,480
