266
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,160
You did it on purpose.

267
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:21,350
You're so mean.

268
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:23,440
Then why didn't you open your eyes earlier?

269
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:24,840
You...

270
00:17:25,070 --> 00:17:25,950
I...

271
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:27,310
All right, I'll stop teasing you.

272
00:17:34,440 --> 00:17:35,320
Chang.

273
00:17:35,790 --> 00:17:37,440
Has Mingshu gotten up?

274
00:17:38,550 --> 00:17:40,070
Mother, I'm up!

275
00:17:40,550 --> 00:17:41,440
Get out now.

276
00:17:41,790 --> 00:17:42,670
Don't let Mother

277
00:17:42,830 --> 00:17:43,870
