332
00:21:01,350 --> 00:21:02,790
Our efforts weren't wasted.

333
00:21:02,920 --> 00:21:05,110
Wen'an must hear this.

334
00:21:05,110 --> 00:21:06,270
Lunch is on me.

335
00:21:06,270 --> 00:21:08,400
We're feasting today!

336
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:09,280
Sure.

337
00:21:21,750 --> 00:21:22,630
Mr. Lu.

338
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:26,440
Congratulations.

339
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:29,150
