needs no formalities.

350
00:21:51,400 --> 00:21:52,590
I'll gladly accept it.

351
00:21:54,720 --> 00:21:55,720
Honestly,

352
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:56,830
now that you've

353
00:21:56,830 --> 00:21:58,390
confessed your feelings for each other,

354
00:21:58,510 --> 00:22:00,070
you should strike while the iron is hot

355
00:22:00,070 --> 00:22:01,590
and marry her quickly.

356
00:22:03,830 --> 00:22:05,880
May your hearts beat as one

357
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:07,240
and your love endure.

358
00:22:07,510 --> 00:22:10,160
May each dawn find your bond

359
00:22:10,160 --> 00:22:11,110
sweeter than nectar.

360
00:22:11,110 --> 00:22:12,510
Enough, enough!

361
00:22:12,510 --> 00:22:13,360
Cheers.

362
00:22:13,380 --> 00:22:14,760
