381
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:10,070
Every notable in the capital

382
00:23:10,070 --> 00:23:11,390
sings her praises, too.

383
00:23:11,830 --> 00:23:14,200
By contrast with Third Lady of Lu,

384
00:23:14,350 --> 00:23:15,440
she's gained

385
00:23:15,550 --> 00:23:17,000
a firm foothold

386
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:18,000
among the noble ladies

387
00:23:18,000 --> 00:23:19,240
and her reputation's soared.

388
00:23:19,480 --> 00:23:21,640
