389
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:22,880
Incredible.

390
00:23:22,880 --> 00:23:25,520
The more incredible thing is yet to come.

391
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:28,880
The old lady

392
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:30,510
is no ordinary woman.

393
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:32,550
She is Consort Chen's birth mother.

394
00:23:33,070 --> 00:23:34,640
For this reason,

395
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:35,960
Consort Chen summoned her to the palace.

396
00:23:36,110 --> 00:23:38,110
Judging by her smug glow,

397
00:23:38,200 --> 00:23:40,040
