401
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:49,200
was raised by some rural physician.

402
00:23:49,480 --> 00:23:51,020
But now, she's navigating

403
00:23:51,030 --> 00:23:52,270
the capital's elite circles with ease,

404
00:23:52,270 --> 00:23:53,720
thriving,

405
00:23:54,290 --> 00:23:55,590
and impressive.

406
00:23:55,590 --> 00:23:56,520
Exactly.

407
00:23:56,750 --> 00:23:58,400
She is far more scheming

408
00:23:58,400 --> 00:23:59,440
than Third Lady of Lu.

409
00:23:59,920 --> 00:24:01,550
Minister Lu must be overjoyed

410
00:24:01,550 --> 00:24:02,830
to gain such a socially

411
00:24:02,830 --> 00:24:04,350
adept daughter overnight.

412
00:24:04,790 --> 00:24:06,030
My father says

413
00:24:06,030 --> 00:24:07,350
he's been

414
