421
00:24:26,750 --> 00:24:28,000
You met His Majesty?

422
00:24:34,750 --> 00:24:36,150
What did he say?

423
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:39,720
He praised my grace and compassion,

424
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:41,760
calling me a "healer's heart"

425
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:45,040
worthy of this era.

426
00:24:45,750 --> 00:24:47,390
Did he really say that?

427
00:24:49,240 --> 00:24:50,120
Father, as you oversee

428
00:24:50,630 --> 00:24:53,240
the construction of the ceremony venue,

429
00:24:53,510 --> 00:24:55,310
I wish to contribute

430
00:24:55,310 --> 00:24:56,680
in your name

431
00:24:56,680 --> 00:24:58,390
