432
00:24:58,510 --> 00:25:00,350
What do you think?

433
00:25:02,680 --> 00:25:05,110
I'm glad that you have such thoughts.

434
00:25:05,960 --> 00:25:07,520
Do as you suggest.

435
00:25:07,960 --> 00:25:09,040
Thank you, Father.

436
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:10,830
If there's nothing else,

437
00:25:11,030 --> 00:25:12,390
I'll take my leave.

438
00:25:13,550 --> 00:25:14,430
Go ahead.

439
00:25:20,750 --> 00:25:21,720
Good.

440
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:25,680
Lady Wan'er has been missing for so long.

441
00:25:25,680 --> 00:25:27,520
