445
00:25:38,070 --> 00:25:40,720
she must've been sent

446
00:25:41,070 --> 00:25:42,200
by either faction.

447
00:25:43,200 --> 00:25:46,590
But if she proves useful,

448
00:25:47,680 --> 00:25:49,550
she's my good daughter.

449
00:25:57,160 --> 00:25:59,720
With her shrewdness,

450
00:25:59,830 --> 00:26:02,000
perhaps we needn't rush

451
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:04,590
to swear loyalty to Prince Rui.

452
00:26:05,830 --> 00:26:06,710
Regarding

453
00:26:07,160 --> 00:26:08,720
her marriage alliance with Lu Chang,

454
00:26:09,030 --> 00:26:10,390
since he resists,

455
00:26:10,750 --> 00:26:12,310
just leave him be.

456
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:15,000
Should Wan'er

457
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:17,760
secure His Majesty's favor,

458
00:26:18,350 --> 00:26:19,590
our family

459
00:26:20,310 --> 00:26:22,630
might survive

460
00:26:23,110 --> 00:26:24,510
the case of Su Changhua

461
00:26:24,510 --> 00:26:26,200
unscathed.

462
00:26:39,550 --> 00:26:40,430
You're here.

463
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:44,110
Last time I was here,

464
00:26:44,720 --> 00:26:46,830
