465
00:26:47,270 --> 00:26:49,000
We made a gentleman's agreement,

466
00:26:49,790 --> 00:26:50,830
but in an instant,

467
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:52,830
you broke it first.

468
00:26:58,750 --> 00:26:59,630
Mr. Song,

469
00:27:01,000 --> 00:27:02,110
regarding this,

470
00:27:03,110 --> 00:27:05,240
