473
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:14,150
Whatever you can do for Mingshu,

474
00:27:14,240 --> 00:27:15,120
I can do, too.

475
00:27:16,240 --> 00:27:18,000
I merely arrived a step behind.

476
00:27:22,200 --> 00:27:23,760
Since Mingshu has chosen you,

477
00:27:24,720 --> 00:27:26,200
from now on, I shall be her friend

478
00:27:27,310 --> 00:27:28,590
and brother.

479
00:27:29,750 --> 00:27:31,390
I've long meant to say this to you.

480
00:27:32,190 --> 00:27:34,440
If you let her suffer even slightly,

481
00:27:35,070 --> 00:27:36,760
