00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:31,590
Mingshu.

489
00:28:38,480 --> 00:28:39,360
Qingzhao.

490
00:28:42,030 --> 00:28:43,150
You've been drinking?

491
00:28:45,880 --> 00:28:46,760
Mingshu,

492
00:28:47,350 --> 00:28:48,280
look at me.

493
00:28:49,440 --> 00:28:50,320
Look at me.

494
00:28:51,640 --> 00:28:52,520
Tell me,

495
00:28:54,510 --> 00:28:56,480
