504
00:29:28,790 --> 00:29:29,670
Qingzhao,

505
00:29:30,590 --> 00:29:31,680
in my eyes,

506
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:32,790
you're perfect.

507
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:34,440
Having you as my friend

508
00:29:34,440 --> 00:29:36,350
is a blessing.

509
00:29:37,510 --> 00:29:39,550
But I'm with Lu Chang now.

510
00:29:39,960 --> 00:29:41,110
You should move on.

511
00:29:43,960 --> 00:29:45,200
Why isn't it me?

512
00:29:47,270 --> 00:29:48,680
Whatever he can do for you,

513
00:29:49,880 --> 00:29:51,920
I can do, too.

514
00:29:52,480 --> 00:29:54,480
- Qingzhao.
- Why isn't it me?

515
00:29:54,590 --> 00:29:55,470
Qingzhao!

516
00:29:56,920 --> 00:29:58,480
Why isn't it me?

517
00:29:58,480 --> 00:29:59,360
Qingzhao.

518
00:30:00,720 --> 00:30:01,600
Qingzhao.

519
00:30:02,030 --> 00:30:03,200
