00:30:16,310 --> 00:30:17,640
Qingzhao, you're drunk.

526
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:18,550
Come home with me.

527
00:30:19,480 --> 00:30:20,720
Why isn't it me?

528
00:30:20,720 --> 00:30:21,600
Wen'an.

529
00:30:23,790 --> 00:30:24,830
Take good care of him.

530
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:26,080
Sure.

531
00:30:28,440 --> 00:30:29,920
