583
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:03,830
I support her choices unconditionally.

584
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:09,790
I knew you'd agree!

585
00:33:12,750 --> 00:33:13,790
- Madam, please enter.
- Please.

586
00:33:13,790 --> 00:33:15,580
(Hualang Pavilion)

587
00:33:18,550 --> 00:33:19,590
On your way here,

588
00:33:19,920 --> 00:33:21,480
did you see the Lu Family's Porridge Shed?

589
00:33:21,680 --> 00:33:23,350
Yes, crowds gathered.

590
00:33:23,350 --> 00:33:24,790
I thought something had happened.

591
00:33:24,960 --> 00:33:26,750
Turns out they built a relief shed

592
00:33:26,750 --> 00:33:27,760
for the refugees.

593
00:33:28,160 --> 00:33:29,110
You didn't hear.

594
00:33:29,280 --> 00:33:30,640
Before Lu Wan'er distributed the porridge,

595
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:32,150
she hired monks for blessings.

596
00:33:32,830 --> 00:33:34,270
Many noble ladies

597
00:33:34,270 --> 00:33:35,680
have joined her charity circle.

598
00:33:35,680 --> 00:33:37,550
Since when do good deeds

599
00:33:37,550 --> 00:33:39,200
require such fanfare?

600
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:40,960
In my opinion,

601
00:33:40,960 --> 00:33:43,000
she's clearly staging a spectacle

602
00:33:43,110 --> 00:33:44,070
to polish her reputation.

603
00:33:44,640 --> 00:33:45,790
Wouldn't onlookers

604
00:33:45,790 --> 00:33:47,400
overwhelm the shed?

605
00:33:47,400 --> 00:33:50,110
Then few refugees

606
00:33:50,110 --> 00:33:51,480
can get the porridge

607
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:52,590
or real help.

608
00:33:56,440 --> 00:33:58,240
Instead of idle talk,

609
00:33:58,480 --> 00:33:59,640
we might as well think

610
00:33:59,640 --> 00:34:01,160
about how to help those refugees.

611
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:02,040
Then,

612
00:34:02,350 --> 00:34:03,790
what can we do?

613
00:34:05,250 --> 00:34:07,830
To ensure their livelihood,

614
00:34:07,830 --> 00:34:10,230
we must look beyond mere handouts.

615
00:34:10,230 --> 00:34:11,110
Mingshu.

616
00:34:12,710 --> 00:34:13,590
Qingzhao.

617
00:34:17,820 --> 00:34:18,820
Mingshu is right.

618
00:34:19,660 --> 00:34:21,380
Porridge feeds them today, not tomorrow.

619
00:34:21,740 --> 00:34:22,940
To solve the problem at its root,

620
00:34:23,420 --> 00:34:25,260
we need to teach them survival skills.

621
00:34:26,340 --> 00:34:27,860
Many women excel at crafts.

622
00:34:27,980 --> 00:34:29,820
Let's teach them to make

623
00:34:29,820 --> 00:34:31,620
Blessing Ceremony items

624
00:34:31,620 --> 00:34:33,020
like sachets

625
00:34:33,020 --> 00:34:34,340
and lanterns

626
00:34:34,620 --> 00:34:35,540
to make money.

627
00:34:36,020 --> 00:34:37,420
This way, they can learn a skill

628
00:34:37,420 --> 00:34:38,340
and make money,

629
00:34:38,340 --> 00:34:40,060
then reinvest the profits into further aid.

630
00:34:41,900 --> 00:34:43,380
That sounds like a good idea.

631
00:34:43,380 --> 00:34:44,220
Later,

632
00:34:44,220 --> 00:34:45,460
I'll propose this to His Highness.

633
00:34:52,430 --> 00:34:53,290
Qingzhao,

634
00:34:54,340 --> 00:34:55,220
are you alright?

635
00:34:56,060 --> 00:34:56,940
Forgive me.

636
00:34:58,380 --> 00:34:59,690
I was drunk and lost my composure that day.

637
00:35:00,140 --> 00:35:01,180
Did I startle you?

638
00:35:03,300 --> 00:35:04,180
No.

639
00:35:06,860 --> 00:35:07,740
Mingshu,

640
00:35:08,900 --> 00:35:10,260
you might laugh,

641
00:35:11,100 --> 00:35:13,060
but my life has been my father's design.

642
00:35:14,020 --> 00:35:15,540
Loving you was

643
00:35:16,300 --> 00:35:17,660
my only act of defiance.

644
00:35:18,780 --> 00:35:20,260
Though the result failed me,

645
00:35:21,140 --> 00:35:22,180
I don't regret it.

646
00:35:22,820 --> 00:35:24,740
Even now, I cannot erase you from my heart.

647
00:35:25,900 --> 00:35:27,700
But I don't want to burden you

648
00:35:28,340 --> 00:35:29,980
or lose your friendship.

649
00:35:31,420 --> 00:35:32,340
Qingzhao,

650
00:35:33,300 --> 00:35:34,380
we've

651
00:35:34,500 --> 00:35:36,300
been through a lot together.

652
00:35:36,940 --> 00:35:38,380
Every time I was in danger,

653
00:35:38,740 --> 00:35:39,740
you stepped ahead

654
00:35:39,740 --> 00:35:40,980
without hesitation.

655
00:35:41,460 --> 00:35:42,460
Your loyalty

656
00:35:42,460 --> 00:35:43,700
is extremely

657
00:35:43,950 --> 00:35:45,460
precious

658
00:35:45,700 --> 00:35:47,100
and worth cherishing.

659
00:35:47,830 --> 00:35:49,300
No matter what,

660
00:35:51,020 --> 00:35:52,180
in my heart,

661
00:35:52,540 --> 00:35:53,560
you'll always

662
00:35:53,940 --> 00:35:55,220
be my most trusted friend.

663
00:35:58,460 --> 00:35:59,940
Then we'll still be friends.

664
00:36:01,550 --> 00:36:02,620
Should Lu Chang

665
00:36:03,140 --> 00:36:04,420
ever wrong you,

666
00:36:04,650 --> 00:36:05,780
feel free to come to me.

667
00:36:06,340 --> 00:36:07,380
I'll stand up for you.

668
00:36:07,660 --> 00:36:08,820
You said it yourself.

669
00:36:09,020 --> 00:36:10,020
Don't go back on your word.

670
00:36:12,220 --> 00:36:13,220
On my honor.

671
00:36:17,660 --> 00:36:20,820
(Shi'an Hall)

672
00:36:26,700 --> 00:36:27,980
There's wasteland near the capital.

673
00:36:28,740 --> 00:36:29,740
The court

674
00:36:30,140 --> 00:36:31,740
contemplates reclamation.

675
00:36:32,420 --> 00:36:33,620
We can

676
00:36:33,780 --> 00:36:34,780
take advantage of this.

677
00:36:35,860 --> 00:36:37,340
How exactly?

678
00:36:38,740 --> 00:36:40,500
Assign refugees to reclaim the land.

679
00:36:40,780 --> 00:36:42,500
Those meeting quotas

680
00:36:42,740 --> 00:36:45,180
retain 10% of cleared land

681
00:36:45,180 --> 00:36:46,340
for private cultivation.

682
00:36:46,340 --> 00:36:47,220
What do you think?

683
00:36:47,940 --> 00:36:50,700
Self-sufficiency through labor.

684
00:36:51,420 --> 00:36:52,940
It sounds like a good idea.

685
00:36:54,980 --> 00:36:57,020
I'll petition His Majesty tomorrow.

686
00:36:59,540 --> 00:37:00,460
In this regard,

687
00:37:00,780 --> 00:37:02,540
Mingshu's sharp mind astounds me.

688
00:37:02,780 --> 00:37:04,980
When we proposed aiding the displaced,

689
00:37:05,100 --> 00:37:06,100
her mind leaped

690
00:37:06,100 --> 00:37:07,700
to crafting trinkets for marketing.

691
00:37:07,700 --> 00:37:09,420
Why can't I think of it?

692
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:10,980
Who said that?

693
00:37:11,860 --> 00:37:13,380
Every time I have a problem,

694
00:37:13,540 --> 00:37:15,510
you give me strategic counsel.

695
00:37:17,300 --> 00:37:18,580
Having you as my consort

696
00:37:18,820 --> 00:37:19,980
makes me feel at ease.

697
00:37:23,340 --> 00:37:24,790
Burdened with great responsibility,

698
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:25,940
Your Highness's every word and deed

699
00:37:25,940 --> 00:37:27,620
shifts thousands of lives.

700
00:37:27,900 --> 00:37:29,260
As your consort,

701
00:37:29,260 --> 00:37:31,380
I should be a capable assistant

702
00:37:31,380 --> 00:37:32,660
and work together with you

703
00:37:32,660 --> 00:37:34,180
on causes beneficial to the people.

704
00:37:38,220 --> 00:37:39,420
I'm blessed

705
00:37:39,580 --> 00:37:41,380
to have a consort like you.

706
00:37:46,100 --> 00:37:48,980
(Hualang Pavilion)

707
00:37:54,650 --> 00:37:55,810
Look at my needlework.

708
00:37:55,810 --> 00:37:56,760
Lovely.

709
00:37:56,760 --> 00:37:57,610
Right?

710
00:37:57,610 --> 00:37:58,530
Her Highness is here.

711
00:38:00,140 --> 00:38:01,020
Your Highness.

712
00:38:04,980 --> 00:38:05,900
You've been working hard.

713
00:38:05,910 --> 00:38:06,820
We just made these.

714
00:38:06,820 --> 00:38:07,700
Have a taste.

715
00:38:08,620 --> 00:38:09,580
- Here.
- Thanks.

716
00:38:18,340 --> 00:38:19,340
Isn't this nice?

717
00:38:20,060 --> 00:38:20,940
It's pretty.

718
00:38:29,420 --> 00:38:30,300
Come.

719
00:38:31,580 --> 00:38:32,460
Here.

720
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:35,340
Have a look.

721
00:38:35,340 --> 00:38:36,970
Prime vegetables, fresh and tender.

722
00:38:37,700 --> 00:38:38,590
Pick freely.

723
00:38:43,060 --> 00:38:44,540
Don't choose lotus roots like this.

724
00:38:44,780 --> 00:38:46,420
Avoid the small ones.

725
00:38:46,420 --> 00:38:47,740
Select those like this.

726
00:38:47,900 --> 00:38:49,540
Note the large pores

727
00:38:49,700 --> 00:38:50,620
and rounded form?

728
00:38:50,620 --> 00:38:52,020
- Such lotus roots taste sweetest.
- I see.

729
00:38:52,700 --> 00:38:53,580
These lotus roots

730
00:38:53,580 --> 00:38:55,540
are my finest,

731
00:38:55,540 --> 00:38:57,140
crisp and succulent.

732
00:38:57,540 --> 00:38:58,420
Here.

733
00:38:59,620 --> 00:39:00,500
All right.

734
00:39:00,620 --> 00:39:01,660
Take care, you two.

735
00:39:01,820 --> 00:39:02,700
Allow me to help.

736
00:39:03,180 --> 00:39:04,060
Thanks.

737
00:39:08,820 --> 00:39:10,820
Thanks for today, Madam Zeng.

738
00:39:11,500 --> 00:39:14,660
(Everlasting Prosperity)

739
00:39:21,020 --> 00:39:23,580
(Everlasting Prosperity)

740
00:39:25,900 --> 00:39:27,340
Greetings, Your Highness.

741
00:39:27,980 --> 00:39:29,060
Your Highness, you summoned me?

742
00:39:29,500 --> 00:39:30,460
Have you

743
00:39:31,300 --> 00:39:32,300
heard of Consort Rui's

744
00:39:32,300 --> 00:39:33,740
relief efforts

745
00:39:34,380 --> 00:39:35,500
through Hualang Pavilion?

746
00:39:35,500 --> 00:39:36,700
(Everlasting Prosperity)

747
00:39:36,700 --> 00:39:37,580
I want to know

748
00:39:38,100 --> 00:39:40,220
your thoughts on this matter.

749
00:39:46,700 --> 00:39:48,220
I know what to do.

750
00:39:49,660 --> 00:39:50,780
I trust no one else

751
00:39:51,380 --> 00:39:52,620
with this task but you.

752
00:39:56,460 --> 00:39:57,380
I'll take my leave.

753
00:39:57,700 --> 00:40:03,140
(Everlasting Prosperity)

754
00:40:05,580 --> 00:40:06,700
Has Your Highness

755
00:40:06,700 --> 00:40:08,300
truly lowered your guard against her?

756
00:40:10,380 --> 00:40:12,100
That depends on whether

757
00:40:12,100 --> 00:40:13,300
she's lowered hers against me.

758
00:40:18,380 --> 00:40:19,660
(One rises as the other falls.)

759
00:40:20,660 --> 00:40:22,020
(If Prince Rui's influence wanes,)

760
00:40:22,460 --> 00:40:24,100
(Prince Yu's rises.)

761
00:40:25,540 --> 00:40:27,900
(How could I boost my enemy's momentum?)

762
00:40:38,700 --> 00:40:39,660
Shall we strike?

763
00:40:43,220 --> 00:40:44,300
Pull your punches.

764
00:40:44,780 --> 00:40:45,700
Don't make it a real blow.

765
00:40:53,620 --> 00:40:54,780
Are you done?

766
00:40:54,780 --> 00:40:55,770
Almost done.

767
00:41:02,900 --> 00:41:03,820
Fire!

768
00:41:04,300 --> 00:41:06,220
Hurry! Move!

769
00:41:07,080 --> 00:41:08,200
Put out the fire!

770
00:41:08,420 --> 00:41:09,380
Put it out!

771
00:41:09,540 --> 00:41:10,620
Where is the water?

772
00:41:11,220 --> 00:41:12,420
Someone help!

773
00:41:12,780 --> 00:41:13,660
Put out the fire!

774
00:41:13,660 --> 00:41:14,580
Just smoke.

775
00:41:15,020 --> 00:41:15,900
It'll be fine.

776
00:41:16,220 --> 00:41:17,520
Come and put out the fire!

777
00:41:28,740 --> 00:41:29,620
Leave us.

778
00:41:37,220 --> 00:41:38,700
If you had handled it properly,

779
00:41:38,980 --> 00:41:40,380
you wouldn't have suffered.

780
00:41:41,980 --> 00:41:43,540
My incompetence

781
00:41:44,140 --> 00:41:45,380
warrants punishment.

782
00:41:47,060 --> 00:41:48,170
I intended to launch a fire attack

783
00:41:48,630 --> 00:41:51,180
while they were off guard.

784
00:41:52,500 --> 00:41:53,900
Had the fire gotten out of control

785
00:41:54,180 --> 00:41:55,300
and displaced the refugees,

786
00:41:55,780 --> 00:41:57,620
Prince Rui would've borne the blame.

787
00:41:58,160 --> 00:41:59,020
Nevertheless,

788
00:41:59,020 --> 00:42:00,180
unexpected exposure

789
00:42:00,980 --> 00:42:02,420
forced our retreat.

790
00:42:10,900 --> 00:42:11,820
Su Tangli,

791
00:42:12,780 --> 00:42:15,060
I know you've always

792
00:42:15,080 --> 00:42:16,620
been cautious.

793
00:42:18,220 --> 00:42:20,020
What caused this lapse?

794
00:42:23,940 --> 00:42:24,820
Your Highness,

795
00:42:26,620 --> 00:42:28,180
are you suspecting me?

796
00:42:52,510 --> 00:42:55,060
♪May heaven and earth show mercy♪

797
00:42:55,060 --> 00:42:57,600
♪Let mortal ties never fade♪

798
00:42:58,830 --> 00:43:01,480
♪As time quietly slips away♪

799
00:43:01,480 --> 00:43:04,560
♪Don't let us miss growing old together♪

800
00:43:05,330 --> 00:43:07,810
♪May this heart stay true as the first day♪

801
00:43:07,810 --> 00:43:11,090
♪I'll wait through blooms and dew♪

802
00:43:11,760 --> 00:43:16,640
♪Let greed and wrath fade with the wind♪

803
00:43:17,810 --> 00:43:20,240
♪May life's towers stand tall♪

804
00:43:20,240 --> 00:43:22,730
♪With love that outlasts all♪

805
00:43:24,140 --> 00:43:26,680
♪Together we'll traverse♪

806
00:43:26,680 --> 00:43:29,860
♪Through grandeur and adversity♪

807
00:43:30,620 --> 00:43:33,080
♪When clarity arrives♪

808
00:43:33,080 --> 00:43:36,490
♪Destiny's threads entwine,
Karma's path refines♪

809
00:43:37,080 --> 00:43:42,280
♪In glances back, our story's told♪

810
00:43:42,830 --> 00:43:46,180
♪If all scenes fade to view♪

811
00:43:46,180 --> 00:43:49,110
♪Will you return♪

812
00:43:49,440 --> 00:43:52,200
♪Through years with sincere love♪

813
00:43:52,200 --> 00:43:55,360
♪May all enigmas grow clear♪

814
00:43:55,640 --> 00:43:58,930
♪Counting endless nights♪

815
00:43:58,930 --> 00:44:01,060
♪Yet never your♪

816
00:44:01,060 --> 00:44:07,150
♪Silhouette in sight♪

817
00:44:08,610 --> 00:44:11,580
♪If the moon above the sea is full♪

818
00:44:11,870 --> 00:44:14,660
♪Will you return♪

819
00:44:15,040 --> 00:44:17,960
♪In years left, wait for me♪

820
00:44:18,120 --> 00:44:21,060
♪With a beginning and an end♪

821
00:44:21,330 --> 00:44:24,360
♪May time inscribe our names♪

822
00:44:24,620 --> 00:44:27,490
♪Where vows remain♪

823
00:44:27,810 --> 00:44:31,340
♪As if it were yesterday♪

